Assign permissions to the Integration user.
From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Users, and then select Users.
Select Analytics Integration User.
Click Permission Set Assignments | Edit Assignments.
Select CRM Analytics for Media SLM.
Add the permission set, and then save your changes.
